body_html:
We primarily use github issues for bugs and installation issues. This is a question better suited for StackOverflow. Please ask it there and tag it with the tensorflow tag. Thanks!

FYI you might be interested in tensorflow/models#325, which says that 0.10.0rc0 has some known performance regressions which should be fixed by the actual release.

We primarily use github issues for bugs and installation issues.  This is a question better suited for StackOverflow.  Please ask it there and tag it with the `tensorflow` tag.  Thanks!

FYI you might be interested in https://github.com/tensorflow/models/issues/325, which says that 0.10.0rc0 has some known performance regressions which should be fixed by the actual release.
